title: Nilüfer Yanya performs "Like I Say (I Runaway)" and more Live on KEXP. Watch the full performance

author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Nilüfer Yanya performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded October 26, 2024.

Songs:
Method Actor
Mutations
Call It Love
Binding
Like I Say (I Runaway)

Nilufer Yanya - Guitar, Vocals
Jazzi Bobbi - Keys, Sax, Synth
Beth O’Lenahan - Bass
Will Archer - Guitar
Ellis Dupuy - Drums

Host: Troy Nelson
Audio Engineer: Kevin Suggs 
Mastering Engineer: Matt Ogaz

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Leah Franks, Emma Juncosa & Ettie Wahl
Editor: Carlos Cruz
